Marketing Brief -- Washington Post Co.:
   Publisher Buys 80% Interest
   In Suburban Maryland Chain
Terms weren't disclosed. Washington Post Co. said its
flagship newspaper, the Washington Post, will continue its
Thursday Montgomery county section, and that the Post and
Gazette papers won't share news or advertising operations.
   Davis L. Kennedy will remain president, publisher and
editor of the Gazette Newspapers, as well as a shareholder of
Gaithersburg Gazette Inc.